@startuml "Logic View - Level 1 (System-to-be)"
!define LIGHTBLUE #87CEFA

' Styling
skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam componentBackgroundColor LIGHTBLUE
skinparam interfaceBackgroundColor LIGHTBLUE

' The REST API interface (consumed by external clients)
() "REST API" as RestAPI

' The central component
component "<<component>>\nLibrary Management\nSystem" as LMS

' APIs consumed by LMS
() "ISBN Retrieval API" as IsbnAPI
() "DB API" as DbAPI

' Connections
RestAPI -- LMS
LMS ..> IsbnAPI : consumes
LMS ..> DbAPI : consumes

note right of LMS
  Provides CRUD operations for:
  - Books
  - Genres
  - Authors
  - Readers
  - Lendings

  Integrates with external services:
  - ISBN retrieval from multiple sources
  - Multiple data storage models
end note

caption Logic View - Level 1 (System-to-be)

@enduml